  "texts": [
    "When combined with other tools like automatic grading, this process stands to become more efficient, less prone to bias, and quicker.",
    "Consequently, the promotion of academic integrity can be achieved by identifying and preventing instances of AIgenerated content, thereby curbing plagiarism and fostering originality in academic endeavors.",
    "Such tools also have the potential to cultivate critical thinking skills.",
    "However, it's imperative to exercise critical thinking in their utilization.",
    "Maintaining human oversight and critically evaluating outputs, particularly in tasks such as essay grading, is indispensable."
  ]
}